#. §0: ```
#. -- if the sum of a sequence of numbers is even, the number of odd numbers in the sequence must be even
#. axiom even_sum_even_odds (A : Multiset Nat) (hA : Even (A.sum)) : Even (A.filter (fun a => Odd a)).card
#. ```
#. §1: `even_sum_even_odds A hA`
#. §2: `A`
#. §3: `∑ (a ∈ A)`
#. §4: `A`
#. §5: `hA`
#: Game.Levels.GraphTheory.L04_OddDegVerts
msgid "§0\n"
"§1 is the proof that the total number of odd numbers in §2 must be even if\n"
"§3 is even.  The hypothesis that the sum of the elements of §4 is even is §5."
msgstr ""

#: Game.Levels.GraphTheory.L04_OddDegVerts
msgid "The Handshake Lemma tells us that the sum of all degrees is even.\n"
"\n"
"Use this fact to show that the number of odd-degree vertices is even."
msgstr ""

